{"tid":1214550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致香港人,不放棄既精神!!","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T04:41:41.000Z","uid":91099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bb52ff8d611a9a2b2b2f7d10f030bb1e910ea18e","tid":1214550,"uid":91099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:41:41.000Z","msg":"大家呢幾日去野餐,辛苦哂!! 香港人除左鐘意打邊爐<br />\n,仲有去野餐嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去完野餐之後,大家都去銀行OR櫃員機撳錢, 呢幾日天氣咁好,去野餐緊係要買多D野食,絕對唔可以馬虎嫁麻,所以大家不妨對換下美金or唔同國家既錢,對率多,自然野食又可以買多D,而我地特別懶,想買野食又唔想下下去櫃員機,緊係要擺係屋企啦.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n但大家唔好拎哂銀行既錢轉哂其他貨幣喎,之後又擺屋企,因為我地既偉大既祖國,如果外匯儲備唔夠,可能會拎香港嘅去用, 香港又冇咁多俾偉大既祖國咁就唔好啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n提外話- 政府支持我地要有公民意識,當然要快D登記做選民啦. 選舉既時候緊係要帶埋老一輩,當然唔少得老人院既親人都一齊去啦.正所謂有票有得揀，冇票冇票傾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\nSorry for 1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}